well... lets see..getting there... that wasnt fun lol. we drove to columbus bc the flight rates are better on tuesday evening... that wasnt bad.. about a 3 hour drive. then we stayed alnght there and were suppose to fly outta there to atlanta for a connection at 9AM. well... the flight was delayed on the count of crew.. so we get to atlanta... but late. so our flight to LA was already boarded. so then they fly us to new york city... hey ive always wanted to go to ny lmao. we almost missed that flight and we wouldve ... but... lindsey took off runnin , she fell flat on her face right in the mddle of the airport it was the funnist thing ever.. and since we gonna miss that flight too nobody said hey are you okay we just said GET UP AND RUN lol so she took offher shoes and went for it. it was hilarious... well we made that flight .. 5 1/2 hour flight from NY to LA ... ugghh lol. we were famous tho lol a stewertist came up to me jesse and lindz and asked if we were the wv girls lmao. well we got to LA at about 7PM there time so it was 1) PM our time. and we get to the hotel and tehre was a wreck and the power was out for 2 blocks lmao . so we walked down to hollywood blvd. and theres somthin goin on across the street. we see the olson twins , chistina milian, and mischa barton & rachel blison * marissa and summer from the OC* , off course my camera is packed  ! ahh i i couldve killed myself for that lol . then were walkin pass the theatre and JC from NSYNC is outside so i talk to him . he was pretty nice... of coure.. no camra.. god ... lol . 
then we go up to the hotel and the power is on ... but were tired so we go to sleep. we got up the next day and went to malibu were like courtney cox, cher, tom cruise... people like that live. we walked down there for a bit then headed to santa monica beach/peir. ahh we had SOOO much fun that day . we had a gymnastic concert on the beach and me and jesse were protectin the pacific ocean against sharks bc we watched the discovery channel on the plane lmao *snaps for mythbusters lmao* the we were tired so we headed back toward the hotel ... ohh we saw Jennifer Aniston in her car. that was sorta exciting and on the way home we saw denzel washionton ... i think hes stalkin me i saw him last year lmao.  that night we went on the blvd. and saw ozzie osborne lmao that was pertty hilaious and we saw these boys break dancin ... tehy were awesome they wre our friends lol we talked to em forever.. then we shopped and on the way back they were gettin arrested lmao that was pretty funny ! well then the next day we got up and toured the waner brothers studio that was sooo awesome ! i swear that was sooo cool ! i saw all ofd the gilmore girls sets and got to go in lukes diner that was cool. saw the real dukes of hazzard car ... then we went in this locked off room and it was the friends set ... central perk ! we got to sit on the couch and everything it was sooo exciting . then we went to rodeo drive.. we got lost lmoa.. who wouldve known that rodeo street didnt run in to rodeo dr. lmao. then we drove up beverly hills ! that was the coolest thing ever !!! we saw, ben stines house, dr phils house , larry kings house, brad pitts house , nick and jessicas house, and were they tape the godfather, and paris hiltons house.... and who konws who else thats just whos the map showed lol. then jesse turned the map upside down to get us home lmoa that was pretty funny * snaps for jesse lol * then we ahd to stop and get kristen a birthday cake ! the cake was adorable!!!! it was her 20th birthday ! so we partied lol . then the next day we just shopped on hollywood blvd./ then flew home that night ! i had sooo much fun tho !! well thats it for now .. im tired lol 

love yah darlin <3 jessica rae
